
Encryption at rest
==================

    - Free of cost
    - Enabled by AWS KMS
    - AES 256 algo
    

    - Encryption is replicated
    - Access to keys are logged
    - Encryption at REST
    - Encrypt once
    - Two Tier Encryption

    Benefits:
    ===========

        - Limit the risk of compromised keys
        - Management
        - Performance
        - Key Rotation

        